name: Futuristic Cityscape #49
description: A neon-lit sci-fi metropolis with sleek skyscrapers, flying vehicles, and an energy core pulsing in the distance. Set against a deep purple-blue night sky with stars and a moon, the cityscape features interconnected buildings with glowing outlines, holographic billboards, and energy transfer beams, creating an immersive vision of a technologically advanced urban future.
